OL,3,CPrison officers call for use of
OL,4,Celectric stun guns
OL,6,FPrison officers are calling on the
OL,7,FJustice Secretary to allow the use of
OL,8,Felectric stun guns in the UK's most
OL,9,Fdangerous jails, following an attack
OL,10,Fby the Manchester bomb plotter on
OL,11,Fthree guards.
OL,13,FMark Fairhurst, national chairman of
OL,14,Fthe Prison Officers' Association
OL,15,F(POA), said they will make the demand
OL,16,Fwhen they meet with Shabana Mahmood on
OL,17,FWednesday, 23 April.
