OL,3,CPrison officers call for use of
OL,4,Celectric stun guns
OL,6,FThe meeting comes after guards at HMP
OL,7,FFrankland in County Durham were
OL,8,Fattacked with hot oil and homemade
OL,9,Fweapons by Hashem Abedi.
OL,11,F"When we face life-threatening
OL,12,Fsituations, we no longer have tactical
OL,13,Foptions," Mr Fairhurst told the BBC,
OL,14,Fsaying officers needed more options if
OL,15,Fextendable batons and synthetic pepper
OL,16,Fspray fail to deal with a situation.
OL,18,F"We want specially trained staff on
OL,19,Fsite who respond to incidents with the
OL,20,Fability to deploy Taser to neutralise
OL,21,Fthat threat.
