OL,3,CPrison officers call for use of
OL,4,Celectric stun guns
OL,6,FThe Prison Service said it will
OL,7,Finvestigate whether frontline staff
OL,8,Fshould be given protective body armour
OL,9,Ffollowing Abedi's attack earlier this
OL,10,Fmonth when four officers were injured.
OL,12,FThe Ministry of Justice has pledged to
OL,13,Fcarry out a review following the
OL,14,Fincident also suspended access to
OL,15,Fkitchens in separation units in
OL,16,Fprisons, where the attack is believed
OL,17,Fto have taken place in Frankland.
OL,19,FMs Mahmood said: "It is clear there
OL,20,Fare further questions to answer, and
OL,21,Fmore that must be done.
