OL,6,F"This will look into how this was able
OL,7,Fto happen, and what we must do to
OL,8,Fbetter protect our prison officers in
OL,9,Fthe future.
OL,11,F"This review will look specifically at
OL,12,Fthis attack, but also more widely at
OL,13,Fhow separation centres are run."
